  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had a-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] sort of like-- well, it was a paper [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] placard with a painting and it had a little door which was opening.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And inside the door were pictures of the Torah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on top there was an apple with a candle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was wearing that as a child, very proud.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But mostly it was the dancing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a lot of dancing in the synagogue, again and again dancing, but with a lot of ecstasy, not just, you know, barely dancing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People were really letting themselves loose in the way they were stomping their feet dancing and singing and-- you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was lots of joy for a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was really a lot-- a lot of happiness.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Pesach was-- probably I remember most, because Pesach was celebrated, you know, at home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had a white shirt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would move up the bed at the front of the table, because according to tradition he is supposed to lean back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of-- of course, asking of the four questions as a child-- and I was the youngest son, so that was very, very enjoyable.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt important, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was something about Pesach-- I'm trying to reach why it was so-- well, the story of Pesach was so fascinating.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not only the asking of the questions, but I understood at that point every word that I was reading in the Haggadah.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
